	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(center)"><sic>Trutee</sic> Room Congregation Bnai Israel</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><date>Tebet the 15th 5617</date>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">At a General Meeting of the members of the above<lb/> Congregation it was unanimously resolved.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Resolved that the thanks of this<lb/> Congregation are due to the <persName>Rev. Isaac Leeser</persName><lb/> for the many favors and assistance rendered<lb/> to the Congn&#59; And the said members highly<lb/> appreciate the various discourses addressed<lb/> to them in their Synagogue&#59; And whereas the<lb/> Revd Gentleman has caused a great impression<lb/> on the mind of the members of this Congn at<lb/> the Consecration of their Synag&#58; by an address<lb/> delivered on that occasion.  Be it resolved<lb/> that to the Said <persName>Rev&#58; Isaac Leeser</persName> as a<lb/> mark of their high respect a Seat for life<lb/> be granted and all privileges as a contributing<lb/> member.  Resolved that a copy of the foregoing<lb/> <sic>he send</sic> to the <persName>Rev. Mr Leeser</persName>&#44; and inserted<lb/> in the Occident.</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">From the minutes</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><placeName>Philada</placeName> <date>Tebet 19&#47;5617 Jany</date>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">the <date>15&#47;1857</date>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">Simon C Noah</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">assist. Secretary</p>
				<p>Rev &#38; Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I have to repeat that in consequence<lb/> of having <sic>hurted</sic> my finger I am prevented in writing<lb/> the above in a more &#38; better suitable style.  You will<lb/> however perceive that the substance of the above emanates<lb/> from the body&#44; and you may add to the above whatever<lb/> you may deem proper&#44; in order that your fame may<lb/> be the better known both here and on the other<lb/> side of the <placeName><sic>atlantic</sic></placeName>&#44; but please to insert it in your next<lb/> number &#38; oblige yours Truly  <persName role="author">Simon C <hi rend="underline">Noah</hi></persName></p>
		</body>
